  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to assess the efficacy and safety of 12 months of treatment
      with 300 IR of STG320 sublingual tablets compared with placebo in adults and adolescents with
      HDM-associated allergic rhinitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
